Morning and evening
Air California has
the only nonstops
between San Diego
and San Jose.
Lowest fare, too.
Now you can choose
from two round trip nonstops
Sunday through Friday plus
28 convenient direct flights a week.
Fly a comfortable Boeing 737.
We've expanded our Suniet
Fleet to give San Diego -
San Jose the easy way.
The thriftv EZ Fare
can save you 20%, even on nonstop
flights. Just check in at the ticket counter 30 minutes
before departure and you'll get the first
available seat on a standby basis
Big savings with our family plan
and economy fares for groups and
military. It's the economical way.
to plan your next weekend
or vacation trip.
Easy going service
from the most fashionably uniformed
cabin attendants in the California sky.
Write your own ticket,
right in your own office. For details on Air
California "Easy Tickets" contact
our local representative.
save
120%
Depart from the easiest gates
at San Diego and San Jose Airports.
Our boarding lounges are just a few
steps from curbside.
Enjoy Beringer Wine
on board plus a fine selection
of premium label cocktails
for only $1.00.
Call Easy Information
for reservations. It's
the most advanced
computerized
reservations/information
system in the airline
industry. If there's an
easier way to get you there,
we'll be the first to tell you.
